                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY.</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Were you ever convicted of felony? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, at Newgate—I do not know how long ago it was—it is within the last twelve months.</p>
